that hydrofoil?

667
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:09,070
I won't
be able to stay with him

668
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:11,450
once they
get out of the harbor.

669
00:41:11,530 --> 00:41:13,120
Those hydrofoils do 40 easy.

670
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,660
Where do you think
they're going?

671
00:41:14,740 --> 00:41:17,950
I've seen that boat
in Macau a couple of times.

672
00:41:18,040 --> 00:41:19,410
That's what I think.

673
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:22,040
Maybe we could get
a head start on them.

674
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:25,000
Well, it's only
an hour's ride in any case.

675
00:42:00,450 --> 00:42:02,160
Macau.

