I heard you right.

682
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,140
What did you say?

683
00:42:19,220 --> 00:42:20,720
They came to the hospital.

684
00:42:20,810 --> 00:42:22,480
One of them
was at the shooting.

685
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:24,100
Look, Ann,

686
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:26,100
why don't you
come in,

687
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:28,400
and we'll take it
to the police?

688
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:29,940
Where are you?

689
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:31,530
Did you
leave the hospital?

690
00:42:31,570 --> 00:42:33,530
Never mind. The police
aren't the answer.

691
00:42:50,460 --> 00:42:51,880
Boat Driver:
Hey, mister,

692
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:54,470
is that the guy
you've been waiting for?

693
00:42:54,550 --> 00:42:55,970
That's him.

694
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:03,980
[ Horn Blowing ]

695
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:08,810
I'll make it worth
your while to wait for me.

696
00:43:08,900 --> 00:43:10,480
You're not going
to rob a casino,

697
00:43:10,570 --> 00:43:11,480
are you?

698
00:43:11,570 --> 00:43:13,190
I don't want to run
a getaway boat.

699
00:43:13,240 --> 00:43:14,360
No, no.

700
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,360
Will you be here,
no matter how late?

701
00:43:16,410 --> 00:43:18,620
I got nothing better
going.

702
00:44:19,180 --> 00:44:20,970
[ Loud Drumming ]

703
00:44:47,700 --> 00:44:49,830
Parade, parade.
Damn. What the hell?

704
00:44:49,920 --> 00:44:52,210
Can't we get out
of here somehow?

705
00:44:52,290 --> 00:44:54,210
Back this thing up
or something.

706
00:44:54,290 --> 00:44:55,840
Man:
There's a taxi behind us.

707
00:44:55,920 --> 00:44:57,510
It will
be ending soon,

708
00:44:57,590 --> 00:44:59,840
and they will move
to another street.

709
00:45:10,560 --> 00:45:11,940
Give them the horn.

710
00:45:12,020 --> 00:45:13,810
Let's get out of here.
Run over 'em.

