00:46:32,890 --> 00:46:35,560
How do you do, Doctor?
Very nice seeing you.

723
00:46:35,650 --> 00:46:38,480
Dr. Land:
And how are you? Sit down.

724
00:46:38,570 --> 00:46:43,110
Well, maybe we don't
need to even count it.

