Steiner:
Carl, duck!

752
00:49:51,603 --> 00:49:53,893
Somebody take care
of the doctor.

753
00:49:53,983 --> 00:49:55,523
Steiner:
Carl, let him go!

754
00:49:55,603 --> 00:49:57,943
Carl, you damn fool,
the fight's tonight!

755
00:49:58,023 --> 00:50:00,363
Carl, come on back here,
