00:50:27,473 --> 00:50:28,843
I recognized.

763
00:50:28,893 --> 00:50:30,643
Stick is right.

764
00:50:30,723 --> 00:50:33,023
There was something
different about that man.

765
00:50:33,063 --> 00:50:34,563
He not only wanted to kill,

766
00:50:34,603 --> 00:50:36,353
he wanted
to punish me as well.

